Capture a payment 
Updated on Oct 24, 2025
Published on Jan 9, 2025
Post
/v3/payments/{payment_id}/capture
Capture authorized payment. Completes payment collection.

Security
HTTP
Type basic
Header parameters
api-version
string
Valid values
[ "2024-11-11" ]
Path parameters
payment_id
string
Required
Min length
39
Max length
39
Example
py-cc3938dc-c2a5-43c4-89d7-7570793348c2
Body parameters

application/json
object
capture_amount
number
The payment amount captured for this payment. Maximum capture amount can only be equal or lesser than the authorized amount value.

Minimum
0.0
Example
10000.0
